      "slug": "mockumentary",
      "title": "Mockumentary",
      "desc": "Facts in disguise.\n\nWhere reality bends and stories wear the mask of truth. These films blur fact and fiction, capturing lives, events, and absurdities with a lens that questions what is real. Humor, satire, and uncanny details emerge, leaving the viewer uncertain, amused, or strangely moved.\n\n\nThis list is not a set of personal recommendations, but a way of cataloging the films I watch. It may also serve as a reference for anyone interested. The list will be updated over time as I discover and view new titles, growing and evolving with each addition.\n\n▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬",
